room_title: Escape room "Narco" by Escapology Lake Elsinore in Temecula
review: I went with a group of 6 people and we were all first timers. We were nervous because we accidently got one of the hardest rooms but the staff was very kind and helpful. The instructions are clear and it was very fun and entertaining. We worked as a team and enjoyed being challenged. Highly recommend!!!

room_title: Escape room "Narco" by Escapology Lake Elsinore in Temecula
review: Great creative rooms Professional and friendly staff! Very fun. I have done 3 of the six rooms. My son has done all 6. Norco room was exceptional and enjoyed Budapest. Under Pressure was no joke hard! Highly recommend!Thank you Eric, Marley,and the rest of the great game hosts!
